FBIS3-44433 "drchi002_k_94007" FBIS-CHI-94-002 Document Type:Daily Report 4 Jan 1994 NATIONAL AFFAIRS Political & Social Yang Shangkun Inscribes Name of Primary School WA0401150694 Beijing Central People's Radio Network in Mandarin 2230 GMT 26 Dec 93 WA0401150694 Beijing Central People's Radio Network Language: Mandarin Article Type:BFN [Summary] The Hope Primary School, constructed with cash donated by children from all over the nation, was inaugurated on 24 December in a village in Pingshan County, Hebei Province. Yang Shangkun wrote the school name.
